    • Method Detail

      • getReference

        java.lang.String getReference(java.lang.Object bo)
        Returns a string that can be used with the ReferenceResolutionService to retrieve the business object. The reference will remain consistent between application executions.
        Parameters:
        bo - the business object for which to retrieve the reference.
        Returns:
        the reference or null if the reference could not be created
        See Also:
        ReferenceResolutionService.getReferencedObject(String)
